---
title: Quick Hoisin Lamb Tacos with Cucumber Slaw & Crispy Shallots
description: This might be our most exciting flavour fusion yet! The humble taco has borrowed a few attributes from a much loved Asian
dish - duck pancakes. Lamb mince is cooked in sticky sweet hoisin sauce before being sandwiched into golden taco shells with
cucumber and crispy shallots. We give it five stars!
